---
title: Sticky Pork Belly Banh Mi with Sesame Fries & Garlic Aioli
description: Take your taste buds on a street food adventure with a crunchy, flavour-packed banh mi! It’s loaded with caramelised pork belly, quick-pickled carrot and creamy sriracha mayo, all tucked into a crusty brioche bun. Served with crispy sesame fries and creamy garlic aioli for dipping, it’s the ultimate fusion feast that’s as fun as it is delicious!
